OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FBritons on a cruise ship hit by a
OL,7,Fhantavirus outbreak are set to be
OL,8,Frepatriated from Tenerife to isolate
OL,9,Fat the hospital used as the UK's
OL,10,Finitial Covid quarantine site, as the
OL,11,FUKHSA said the risk to the public
OL,12,F"remains very low".
OL,14,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,15,Fsaid British MV Hondius passengers
OL,16,Fwill be transferred to an isolation
OL,17,Ffacility at Arrowe Park Hospital on
OL,18,Fthe Wirral, Merseyside, after being
OL,19,Frepatriated to the UK on a chartered
OL,20,Fflight.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
