CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FThe cruise ship, containing 22 British
OL,7,Fpassengers and crew, is expected to
OL,8,Freach Tenerife, one of Spain's Canary
OL,9,FIslands, early on Sunday morning.
OL,11,FThe UKHSA said on Saturday evening
OL,12,Fthat the risk to the general public
OL,13,F"remains very low".
OL,15,FOfficials from the UKHSA and Foreign
OL,16,FOffice will greet the MV Hondius when
OL,17,Fit docks in Tenerife, with Britons on
OL,18,Fboard tested for hantavirus before
OL,19,Fthey disembark.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FIf people test negative and are not
OL,7,Fdisplaying symptoms, they will be
OL,8,Ftaken straight to a chartered
OL,9,Frepatriation flight staffed by medical
OL,10,Fprofessionals and containing personal
OL,11,Fprotective equipment such as face
OL,12,Fmasks.
OL,14,FAfter returning to the UK, the
OL,15,Fpassengers will be housed in an
OL,16,Faccommodation block on the Arrowe Park
OL,17,Fsite away from the hospital's public
OL,18,Fareas to receive clinical assessments
OL,19,Fand testing as a precautionary measure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FThe hospital was used to house British
OL,7,Fcitizens returning from Wuhan, China,
OL,8,Fin January 2020 at the start of the
OL,9,FCovid pandemic.
OL,11,FThe World Health Organisation (WHO)
OL,12,Fsaid on Saturday that there were
OL,13,Fcurrently no symptomatic passengers on
OL,14,Fboard the ship.
OL,16,FThe UN health agency said there had
OL,17,Fbeen six confirmed hantavirus cases
OL,18,Flinked to MV Hondius and that four
OL,19,Fpatients were currently in hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
