OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FIt added that a total of eight cases,
OL,7,Fincluding three deaths, had been
OL,8,Freported ` with one previous suspected
OL,9,Fcase being reclassified after testing
OL,10,Fnegative for hantavirus.
OL,12,FThe UKHSA said three British nationals
OL,13,Fare included in the eight cases ` two
OL,14,Finvolve confirmed hantavirus and
OL,15,Fanother one is suspected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
