PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FThe two confirmed British cases are in
OL,7,Fhospital in South Africa and the
OL,8,FNetherlands, while the third British
OL,9,Fnational disembarked from the ship on
OL,10,FTristan da Cunha, where they live and
OL,11,Fis being supported by health services
OL,12,Fon the remote South Atlantic island.
OL,14,FProfessor Robin May, chief scientific
OL,15,Fofficer atUKHSA, said: "We continue
OL,16,Fto work at pace with our international
OL,17,Fpartners to ensure the safe
OL,18,Frepatriation of British nationals from
OL,19,Fthe MV Hondius.
OL,26,@wD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
