PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,F"The safety and wellbeing of those on
OL,7,Fboard remains our number one priority.
OL,8,FEstablished infection control measures
OL,9,Fwill be in place at every step of the
OL,10,Fjourney, and passengers will receive
OL,11,Ffull support throughout, including
OL,12,Fduring their period of isolation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
