CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FJanelle Holmes, the chief executive of
OL,7,FWirral University Teaching Hospital
OL,8,FNHS Foundation Trust, said in a letter
OL,9,Fto staff: "We have been asked by NHS
OL,10,FEngland and the UK Health Security
OL,11,FAgency (UKHSA) to house the guests,
OL,12,Frecognising how quickly and positively
OL,13,Fwe responded to and supported the
OL,14,Frepatriation of British nationals from
OL,15,FWuhan and the Diamond Princess prior
OL,16,Fto the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,26,@qD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
