OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,F"We will be welcoming the guests on
OL,7,FSunday May 10 2026 and they will all
OL,8,Fbe screened for symptoms before they
OL,9,Farrive on site; nobody showing any
OL,10,Fsymptoms will be transferred here.
OL,12,F"If anyone becomes unwell after
OL,13,Farrival, they will be transferred
OL,14,Fquickly to another facility."
OL,16,FEmergency services in the north west
OL,17,Fof England said they expected the
OL,18,Fpassengers to be kept in a "managed
OL,19,Fsetting" for up to 72 hours.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@]O]zD@\OU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
