CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FPublic health specialists will then
OL,7,Fassess whether they can isolate at
OL,8,Fhome or at another suitable location
OL,9,Fbased on their living arrangements.
OL,11,FBritons returning to the UK will stay
OL,12,Fin self-isolation for 45 days and will
OL,13,Fnot be allowed to take public
OL,14,Ftransport to their homes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
