OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,F"In line with advice from the UK
OL,7,FHealth Security Agency, on arrival,
OL,8,Fthey will be taken to a managed
OL,9,Fsetting for clinical assessment and
OL,10,Ftesting. We expect this initial stay
OL,11,Fto be up to 72 hours.
OL,13,F"Following this, public health
OL,14,Fspecialists will assess whether they
OL,15,Fcan isolate at home or at another
OL,16,Fsuitable location, based on their
OL,17,Fliving arrangements.
OL,19,F"The risk to the general population
OL,20,Fremains very low."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
