OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FWHO has sought to reassure "worried"
OL,7,FTenerife residents that they will not
OL,8,Fencounter passengers of the hantavirus-
OL,9,Fhit cruise ship set to dock on their
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FIn a letter addressed to the people of
OL,13,FTenerife, WHO director-general Dr
OL,14,FTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus said he
OL,15,Fknew residents were "worried".
OL,17,FHe said the virus was "serious" but
OL,18,Fthe outbreak was "not another Covid"
OL,19,Fand the "current public health risk
OL,20,Ffrom hantavirus remains low".
OL,26,@nD@\OUnD@dO]wD@UOUwD@]O]yD@WOUyD@_O]zD@
OL,26,AROUzD@dO]{D@IOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
