FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778447474
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus-hit ship set to
OL,4,Cbe repatriated to UK from Tenerife
OL,6,FHe added: "Spain's authorities have
OL,7,Fprepared a careful, step-by-step plan:
OL,8,Fpassengers will be ferried ashore at
OL,9,Fthe industrial port of Granadilla, far
OL,10,Ffrom residential areas, in sealed,
OL,11,Fguarded vehicles, through a completely
OL,12,Fcordoned-off corridor, and repatriated
OL,13,Fdirectly to their home countries."
OL,15,FThe outbreak has been connected to a
OL,16,Fbirdwatching expedition in Argentina
OL,17,Fthat two of the passengers went on
OL,18,Fbefore boarding the ship.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
